We shouldn't have a separate registration flow for health. It should be the same as any other endpoint:

```
@tchannel.thrift.register(Meta)
def health(request):
    return HealthStatus(ok=True)
```

We already register the "not found" handler by default, this could go there: https://github.com/uber/tchannel-python/blob/master/tchannel/tornado/dispatch.py#L67

